claim.claim-text:
A thin film transistor (TFT) of a display apparatus, the TFT (100; 500) comprising:
an active layer (110; 510; 570) disposed on a substrate;
a first gate electrode (120; 520; 560) disposed to overlap the active layer, the first gate electrode branching as a plurality of lines (520a, 520b; 560a, 560b);
a gate insulator (150; 550) disposed between the active layer and the first gate electrode; and
a source electrode (130; 530) and a drain electrode (140; 540) respectively disposed at both ends of the active layer,
wherein the active layer (110; 510: 570) comprises:
one or more channel areas (112; 512; 572) disposed between the source electrode and the drain electrode;
one or more dummy areas (114; 514; 574), a length of each of the one or more dummy areas extending from an edge of a corresponding channel area (112; 512; 572); and
a plurality of link areas (116; 516; 576) disposed between the one or more channel areas (112; 512; 572) to connect the one or more channel areas in one pattern.
